    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1410274848" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1410274848" />
    <a title="Man Grover" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/47675244-man-grover"><img alt="Man Grover" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1410274848?book_show_action=true">Oct 06, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Man Grover" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Man Grover" href="/user/show/47675244-man-grover">Man Grover</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1410274848" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2626932680271973874">When a philosopher decides to write a thriller, the result is this fast paced , action packed book with deep insights into the human condition.<br/>Richard Botelho has taken pages out of today&apos;s headlines and combined them with science fiction and philosophy. The result is at once uplifting and absorbing. This is an elegant story teller who is also brilliant at playing with words.<br/>I highly recommend this book.</span>
  <span id="freeText2626932680271973874" style="display:none">When a philosopher decides to write a thriller, the result is this fast paced , action packed book with deep insights into the human condition.<br />Richard Botelho has taken pages out of today's headlines and combined them with science fiction and philosophy. The result is at once uplifting and absorbing. This is an elegant story teller who is also brilliant at playing with words.<br />I highly recommend this book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="2626932680271973874" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


