              <span id="reviewTextContainer1434818589" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15358671934953731583">This frighteningly plausible premise will leave you questioning our world. Deeply provocative and richly detailed, Richard Botelho paints a remarkable picture of incomparable depth. The powerfully driven narrative takes the reader on a chilling and fascinating journey. Beautifully written, this book will pique your curiosity and leave your spine tingling. A brilliant work of....fiction? </span>

          </span>
        </div>


