<span id="freeTextContainer13260728991105800363">Reason for Existence is outstanding! It covers a couple of genres, mainly Science fiction, politics, and romance. David Jordan is planted on the earth ready to initiate and influence humans towards a peaceful life, even if they are targeted by his alien nemesis, Eric Waller and the Illicks. David was able to help the humans before they attempt destroy themselves with nuclear or biological bombs. The humans were unaware that the aliens were able to neutralize the bombs to preserve life, but it wo</span>
  <span id="freeText13260728991105800363" style="display:none">Reason for Existence is outstanding! It covers a couple of genres, mainly Science fiction, politics, and romance. David Jordan is planted on the earth ready to initiate and influence humans towards a peaceful life, even if they are targeted by his alien nemesis, Eric Waller and the Illicks. David was able to help the humans before they attempt destroy themselves with nuclear or biological bombs. The humans were unaware that the aliens were able to neutralize the bombs to preserve life, but it would not be life as we know it now. <br />David’s greatest search was to understand the emotions that humans have, namely the feeling of love. Just as he was about to expound on love and express the love he has for his girlfriend Jenny, she is killed in a plane crash caused by Eric Waller. He then understands the true feelings of love, and what it means to lose it. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="13260728991105800363" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
