<div id="review_1463192375" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1463192375" />
    <a title="Jackie Rogers" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/33443462-jackie-rogers"><img alt="Jackie Rogers" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1454531770p2/33443462.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1463192375?book_show_action=true">Dec 08, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jackie Rogers" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jackie Rogers" href="/user/show/33443462-jackie-rogers">Jackie Rogers</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1463192375" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18261142667838781936">Enter extraterrestrial David Jordan. Main character in this thought provoking book. David is sent to earth to befriend Nicholas Straka. They find themselves embroiled with an evil race that is determined to eradicate humanity. The fight is on with others drawn in to this battle. Has a little romance between David and a human young woman. Held my interest and went rather fast. Thank you to Richard Botelho and Goodreads.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

