              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3285862894669285354">The world is on the brink of World War III. The Secretary General of the United Nations calls on a businessman to resolve an escalating nuclear crisis. Only the businessman isn&apos;t human. He is an alien living on Earth to observe humans.<br/><br/>Very different type of book. Not an action novel. More philosophical and has events a little too close to current day.</span>
